machine_start_gcode.value:
""  if machine_gcode_flavor == "UltiGCode" else ";material_bed_temperature={material_bed_temperature} material_print_temperature={material_print_temperature} material_print_temperature_layer_0={material_print_temperature_layer_0}
M190 S{material_bed_temperature_layer_0}
M104 T0 S{material_standby_temperature, 0}
M104 T0 S{material_print_temperature_layer_0, 0}
G21 ;metric values
G90 ;absolute positioning
M82 ;set extruder to absolute mode
M107 ;start with the fan off
M200 D0 T0 ;reset filament diameter
M200 D0 T1
G28 ;home all
T1 ; move to the nozzle 2
G0 Z20 F2400 ;move the platform to 30mm
M109 T1 S{material_print_temperature_layer_0, 1}
G0 X210 Y20 F7200
G92 E0
G92 E-7.0 ;prime distance
G1 E0 F45 ;purge nozzle
G1 E-6.5 F1500 ; retract
T0 ; move to the nozzle 1
M104 T1 S{material_standby_temperature, 1}
G0 Z20 F2400
M109 T0 S{material_print_temperature_layer_0, 0}
G0 X210 Y20 F7200
G92 E0
G92 E-7.0
G1 E0 F45 ;purge nozzle
G1 E-6.5 F1500
M104 T0 S{material_standby_temperature, 0}
T{initial_extruder_nr} ;switch to the first nozzle used for print
M109 T{initial_extruder_nr} S{material_print_temperature_layer_0, initial_extruder_nr}
M400 ;finish all moves
G1 E0 F1500
G92 E0
;end of startup sequence
"

machine_end_gcode.value:
""  if machine_gcode_flavor == "UltiGCode" else "G90 ;absolute positioning
M104 S0 T0 ;extruder heater off
M104 S0 T1
M140 S0 ;turn off bed
T0 ; move to the first head
M107 ;fan off"
